{"tid":708211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有濕疹 長期病既入一入黎","createTime":"2018-06-19T07:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T15:52:11.000Z","uid":73407,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef7c538107adde96c4015c65dac7b8fb6c98c2b","tid":708211,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j68jUv0h2wY?t=11m41s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj68jUv0h2wY%3Ft%3D11m41s&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9ff12551\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j68jUv0h2wY?t=11m41s</a><br />\n呢個Youtuber 有異位性皮膚炎 係其中一種最常見既濕疹<br />\n<br />\n佢個治療方法未必對每個人有用<br />\n但係佢對長期病患者既說話講得好好<br />\n<br />\n唔好比個病定義自己既人生<br />\n揾一個病人以外既身分做到最好<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要霍金咁偉大<br />\n因為一個無病無痛既人都未必做到"},{"pid":"0778e48a0e8629283c55f22cef3b27e3c16f3920","tid":708211,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c2797d28f2e67be249efbfc777693ba26392c40","tid":708211,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0b1f5995ae4237ffd8ce3ec01a8d283800e0321","tid":708211,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188f4d428740a8db532723799dda3cc1c8e837cc","tid":708211,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"佢係死者男友？<br />\n咁快手做白事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"1dabc1f09742b5b0810a76ba1c63a5df53af5b5f","tid":708211,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"188f4d428740a8db532723799dda3cc1c8e837cc","tid":708211,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"佢係死者男友？<br />\n咁快手做白事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRIP"},"ci